Vendored for spec 011 (Warm-Modern Facelift) per FR-003.

NOTE: This directory ships the LICENSE marker. The actual subsetted WOFF2 file
(Latin-1 + digits + symbols subset, weight 400) MUST be placed at
jetbrains-mono-regular.woff2 by an operator with network access. Until then,
the @font-face declaration in tokens.css will fail to fetch and the browser
will fall back to monospace system stack. Documented in
specs/011-warm-modern-facelift/implementation-notes.md.
